title: Top 10 QB Rankings + Preseason Takeaways, UDK FOR LIFE! - Fantasy Football Podcast for 8/15
description:
On today’s fantasy football podcast, back into player rankings debates with the top 10 quarterbacks for the 2022 season! Which elite QBs are going too high in fantasy football drafts? Are there any draft values in the top 10? Plus, NFL News and fantasy takeaways from Preseason Week 1! Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for August 15th, 2022
